name: CHISCKEN STRISPS
description:
born from thoughts upon eating the last chicken strip in the box of chicken strips

made with bitsy hd at like 4 am when i should have been sleeping but was instead eating chicken strips. 

i do not want to make a bitsy game ever again it was a terrible time and none of the hacks that were supposed to make it a less terrible time worked properly. the game is not fun. i do not want people to think this is the content i want to make. any bugs in this will be considered a good thing as it will discourage people from playing it.  i have no more chiscken strisps :(
